# Adzuna API credentials
# Get your free keys at: https://developer.adzuna.com/
# 1. Sign up at https://developer.adzuna.com/
# 2. Create an application to get your app_id and app_key
# 3. Copy this file to .env and fill in your values

VITE_ADZUNA_APP_ID=your_app_id_here
VITE_ADZUNA_APP_KEY=your_app_key_here
